    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_3_3351-3378",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3351-3378",
      "markText": "三类现象：（1）稀缺性，（2）不确定性，（3）复杂性。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3351&rangeEnd=3378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3351&rangeEnd=3378"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_11399-11481",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "11399-11481",
      "markText": "法玛（Eugene F.Fama）由于确立了金融市场有效性假设而分享诺贝尔经济学奖，他指出，一个理论被称为“好的”，如果它满足三项条件——简单性、统一性、可证伪性。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11399&rangeEnd=11481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11399&rangeEnd=11481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_1680-1698",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1680-1698",
      "markText": "有稀缺就有竞争，并且有竞争就有歧视。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1680&rangeEnd=1698",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1680&rangeEnd=1698"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_6371-6423",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6371-6423",
      "markText": "张五常“街头巷尾观察世界”几十年修成的功夫，使他能从人们的行为（变量）准确推测诱致了这些行为的社会制度。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6371&rangeEnd=6423",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6371&rangeEnd=6423"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_3_1309-1370",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1309-1370",
      "markText": "中国的经济学研究十分落后，主要由于教育与科研管理体制的极端官僚化，或许，中国的经济学研究正以加速度落后于西方的经济学研究。",
      "totalCount": 40,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1309&rangeEnd=1370",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1309&rangeEnd=1370"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_411-449",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "411-449",
      "markText": "核心观念的展开，就是理论。因此，研读任何一套理论，最快捷的方式就是直入核心。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=411&rangeEnd=449",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=411&rangeEnd=449"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_3764-3832",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3764-3832",
      "markText": "小密尔首先是逻辑学家，英文表达具有严谨的逻辑感，他定义了“价值”（values）——被感受到的重要性（importance felt）。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3764&rangeEnd=3832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3764&rangeEnd=3832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_5632-5665",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5632-5665",
      "markText": "仅当幸存者被经济学家观察到的时候，幸存者的行为被赋予经济学的理性。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5632&rangeEnd=5665",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5632&rangeEnd=5665"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_5_4997-5067",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4997-5067",
      "markText": "极端而言，对于特定问题有完备理性的行为主体，“能力—困难”差距等于零。在另一极端，完全没有理性能力的行为主体，“能力—困难”差距趋于无穷大。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4997&rangeEnd=5067",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4997&rangeEnd=5067"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_8_29377-29392",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "29377-29392",
      "markText": "权力就是将成本加给他人的能力。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=29377&rangeEnd=29392",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=29377&rangeEnd=29392"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_2461-2557",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2461-2557",
      "markText": "罗和德布鲁证明的“福利经济学第二基本定理”，提供了这样的承诺，即通过改变初始资源禀赋（包括财产权利）在社会成员当中的分布，可以使完全竞争市场经济的一般均衡恰好是社会福利最大化所需的帕累托状态。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2461&rangeEnd=2557",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2461&rangeEnd=2557"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_3134-3211",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3134-3211",
      "markText": "假如世界充满着不确定性，那么，行为主体的每一行为的全部可能后果，应依照这些后果使行为主体满意的程度排列在横轴上，这些后果的发生概率，于是形成一条分布曲线。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3134&rangeEnd=3211",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3134&rangeEnd=3211"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_6149-6198",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6149-6198",
      "markText": "经济学解释可从假说开始，但必须始终坚持内生于模型的变量具有很好的可观测性，于是能推演出可检验的命题",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6149&rangeEnd=6198",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6149&rangeEnd=6198"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_8137-8168",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "8137-8168",
      "markText": "如果偏好是稳定不变的，为什么一些人比另一些人更喜欢听古典音乐？",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8137&rangeEnd=8168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=8137&rangeEnd=8168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_4_10707-10785",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "10707-10785",
      "markText": "这一假说具有足够的普遍性；其次，是否下雨，这是可观测的；第三，如果某一天，虽然不下雨，我却看到一片乌云飘过，那么，我知道我必须修正我的假说，因为出现了反例。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=842316&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10707&rangeEnd=10785",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6eb32be05cda4c6eb68f0d0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=10707&rangeEnd=10785"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "842316_6_11387-11460",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11387-11460",
      "markText": "人们倾向于高估小概率事件的权重——即给予客观概率很小的各种事件过高的（超过客观概率的）重要性感受，同时倾向于低估大概率和中等概率的各种事件的权重。",
      "totalCount": 32,
